    >doc malloc
      -> $p$stdlib.sheet\|malloc -------------------------------$$
      -> 
      -> $|$\|malloc\|$$
      -> $|$\|allocate\|memory\|dynamic memory\|$$
      -> void* malloc(size_t size)
